(Sorry, everybody. I was grounded and when I got ungrounded, hotmail 
wouldn't let me in. But I'm back now, and my mom promised to be easier on 
me.)

Key lunges out from behind the trees (in her beast mode), tackling Plintissa 
away from Liono and biting at her.

Blue Stinger lands near Ramhorn, she starts dragging him to the CR chamber 
when Antagony catches up to her and helps her. In between them, the two 
girls carry Ramhorn to the CR chambers.

Sona flies in behind Shocker, firing at him.
